            <div >
			 <p><b>Foundation course material includes:</b></p>
			  <ol type="a">
               <li>Learning through the Study guides - Ten hours</li>
               <li>Practice through Exercises:
                 <ul><br/>
                   <li>Chapter tests - Two hours</li>
                   <li>Fill in the Blanks - Two hours</li>
                   <li>Evaluation test- Two hours </li>
                 </ul>
               </li>
